{"article_id":"NZ9cZm3PNMwhYcUA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Turkey has given its first official statement","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"on how","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"it believes","depth":12},{"id":3,"text":"Saudi writer Jamal Khashoggi was killed ,","depth":12},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"he was immediately strangled .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"The statement follows weeks of media reports about the murder at the Saudi consulate in Istanbul on 2 October .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Turkey has yet to provide evidence .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Chief prosecutor Irfan Fidan said","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"meetings with his Saudi counterpart this week led to `` no concrete results '' .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The Turkish statement said :","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"`` In accordance with plans made in advance ,","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"the victim , Jamal Khashoggi , was choked to death","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"immediately after entering the Consulate General of Saudi Arabia . ''","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"His body was then dismembered and destroyed `` again , in line with advance plans '' ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"it added .","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"Khashoggi ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"a Saudi national","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"working for the US press ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"was a well-known critic of his home country 's rulers .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"His body has not been found ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"but Turkey , the US and Saudi Arabia have all agreed","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that he was killed at the consulate .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Turkey said","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"it had put three main questions to the Saudis during the prosecutor 's visit :","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"Do they have any new information about the planning of the killing ?","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"An unnamed Saudi official previously told Reuters news agency","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that Khashoggi 's body had been rolled in a rug","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"and given to a `` local co-operator '' ,","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"who disposed of it .","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"On Wednesday , the delegation responded the questions in writing ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"according to Turkey .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Saudi Arabia said","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"the answers could only come from a joint investigation .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"It also noted","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that it had never given an official statement on the existence of a `` co-operator '' .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Turkey has steered away from publicly blaming Saudi Arabia for the killing .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"However , a senior spokesperson from the ruling AK Party said on Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that it could not have been carried out","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"without orders from someone in a senior position .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan spoke to Saudi King Salman last week ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and the two agreed to continue co-operating in the investigation .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Unnamed Turkish officials have previously told media outlets","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that they had audio and visual evidence","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to prove their accounts of the writer 's death ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"but nothing has been released .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Turkish media have published details on how sources say","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Khashoggi was killed ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"including allegations","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"he was tortured .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"His Turkish fiancée , Hatice Cengiz , gave a tearful interview to local television last week ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"she would never have let her partner enter the consulate","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"if she had thought","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that the `` Saudi Arabia authorities would hatch a plot ''","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"to kill him .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"He had entered the consulate","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to sort out documents for their marriage .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Attorney General Sheikh Saud al-Mojeb met Mr Fidan twice ,","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"visited the consulate","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"and spoke with Turkey 's intelligence agency during his visit to Istanbul this week .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"He flew back to Saudi Arabia on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"without making an official statement .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Saudi Arabia has changed its account","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"of what happened to Khashoggi .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"When he first disappeared ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"it said","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Khashoggi had walked out of the building alive .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"It later admitted","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"he had been murdered ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the killing was premeditated and a result of a `` rogue operation '' .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Saudi Arabia has subsequently said","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that Khashoggi was murdered ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and that it is `` determined to find out all the facts '' .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"It has arrested 18 suspects ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"who ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"it says ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"will be prosecuted in Saudi Arabia .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Turkey wants the suspects to be extradited .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Saudi Arabia has faced backlash over the death , including from its allies ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"who have called for answers .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"President Donald Trump has said","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"he is `` not satisfied '' with the Saudi account .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"However , he also said","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"he was unwilling to sacrifice lucrative arms deals with the country .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Meanwhile , US activists have launched a petition ,","depth":3},{"id":87,"text":"calling for a section of road near the Saudi embassy in Washington to be renamed Jamal Khashoggi Way .","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"On Wednesday , France 's foreign minister Jean-Yves Le Drian said","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"Khashoggi 's death was a `` crime '' and `` odious '' .","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"France was not `` dependent on our economic relations with Saudi Arabia ''","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"and the country would impose sanctions ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"but no details were given .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"UK Foreign Secretary Jeremy Hunt also said","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"it was an appalling act ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"adding","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"that it had `` possibly '' given the US and the UK a chance","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"to put new pressure on Saudi Arabia over other issues .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Earlier in the day , the US called for a swift cessation of hostilities in Yemen ,","depth":3},{"id":100,"text":"where a Saudi-led coalition has been fighting local Houthi rebels .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":188,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":186,"right":187,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":163,"right":185,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":158,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":123,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":108,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":6,"relation":"contex